    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Protection-Consultative meetings with key GON stakeholders for NMS and SOPs; Trainings on victim protection  procedures; Legal, psychosocial, and medical support given to victims of trafficking; Shelters assessed using the monitoring system developed; Research to inform policy on human trafficking\r\n\t\r\n\t\tProsecution- Training modules for judicial and law enforcement agencies developed;  Trainings on SOPs for investigation, prosecution, and adjudication of TIP cases; Trainings on Foreign Employment Act; Trainings on the central database system given to the police\r\n\t\r\n\t\tPrevention-Awareness raising on the prevention of human trafficking and unsafe migration  to community members, local government, and law enforcement agencies; Trainings on safe migration and career counseling ; trainings on financial planning given to families of the most disadvantaged communities"
      },
      "ne": null
